{"tid":2506750,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"全球提款機 - 蘋果公司 遭俄羅斯罰款1200萬美元 歐盟、德國反壟斷法在後","createTime":"2021-04-27T13:25:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T05:46:51.000Z","uid":1086,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"de6c97203bfeb57fee8f9fadb83d1d7a48db38e3","tid":2506750,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T13:25:55.000Z","msg":"莫斯科（路透社）-俄羅斯聯邦反壟斷服務局（FAS）週二表示，已對美國科技巨頭蘋果公司處以1200萬美元的罰款，原因是蘋果涉嫌濫用其在市場上的主導地位。<br />\nFAS表示，蘋果通過其iOS操作系統分發的移動應用程序使自己的產品具有競爭優勢。<br />\n<br />\n德國廣告協會（ZAW）其中 9 個產業代表發起投訴，成員包括 Facebook 和媒體巨頭 Axel Springer。ZAW 認為，蘋果的 ATT 功能濫用市場力量，並違背反壟斷法，「蘋果透過該舉動有效將競爭對手排除在其生態系統之外，但自家的廣告服務卻又能不受影響，繼續收集大量的用戶數據」。<br />\n<br />\n歐盟主管競爭事務的官員維斯塔格（Margrethe Vestager）將在本周指控蘋果公司（Apple Inc.）針對開發商的App Store政策違反歐盟法，涉及不公平的市場競爭。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-russia-apple-fine/russian-competition-watchdog-fines-apple-12-million-for-abusing-dominant-position-idUSKBN2CE1IR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-russia-apple-fine%2Frussian-competition-watchdog-fines-apple-12-million-for-abusing-dominant-position-idUSKBN2CE1IR&d=1Ie%2FqJFF6iBMyzR%2B2a49oJ1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=e0d56f66\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-russia-apple-fine%2Frussian-competition-watchdog-fines-apple-12-million-for-abusing-dominant-position-idUSKBN2CE1IR&h=6a79a486\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/us-russia-apple-fine/russian-competition-watchdog-fines-apple-12-million-for-abusing-dominant-position-idUSKBN2CE1IR</a>"},{"pid":"3cd8b152e59345bf09ce9d5c71eaded2ced80e54","tid":2506750,"uid":370409,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T13:27:08.000Z","msg":"十年後到Tesla"},{"pid":"d87806a1b25c574137d479344302e5e37df8c41e","tid":2506750,"uid":281306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T13:28:14.000Z","msg":"ATT咁都濫用市場力量<img src=\"/